368
00:14:24,570 --> 00:14:25,170
Thank you.

369
00:14:25,650 --> 00:14:27,290
So that's how easy it is to add

370
00:14:27,290 --> 00:14:29,670
a new person to an ongoing conversation.

371
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:31,870
And so often we end up having very

372
00:14:31,870 --> 00:14:34,310
